Package: VegChangeR
Title: Vegetation Change Analysis Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Gergo", family = "Dioszegi", email = "dijogergo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive tool for analyzing vegetation changes over time using
    stacked (time series) satellite imagery-obtained raster data. Supports multiple time scales and memory-optimized processing.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DijoG/VegChangeR
BugReports: https://github.com/DijoG/VegChangeR/issues
